### Users API Endpoints
### Base URL: https://localhost:7001/api/v1
### Requires authentication - run auth.http login first

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001/api/v1
@contentType = application/json
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

### Login first to get auth token
# @name loginRequest
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### Store the token
@authToken = Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.accessToken}}
@adminUserId = {{loginRequest.response.body.userId}}

### ============================================
### User Queries
### ============================================

### Search all users
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### Search users with query
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?search=admin
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### Search users with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### Get user by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{adminUserId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### ============================================
### User Profile Management
### ============================================

### Update user profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/{{adminUserId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstName": "Admin",
  "lastName": "User",
  "title": "System Administrator",
  "phoneNumber": "555-000-0001"
}

### ============================================
### User Status Management
### ============================================

### Register a test user first
# @name registerRequest
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "testuser@test.com",
  "password": "TestUser123!",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User"
}

@testUserId = {{registerRequest.response.body}}

### Activate user
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/{{testUserId}}/activate
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### Deactivate user
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/{{testUserId}}/deactivate
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### ============================================
### Role Assignment
### ============================================

### Assign role to user (use a valid roleId from GET /roles)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/{{testUserId}}/roles
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "roleId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### Remove role from user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/{{testUserId}}/roles/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### ============================================
### Test Scenarios
### ============================================

### Get non-existent user (should fail with 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000099
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### Update user without auth (should fail with 401)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/{{adminUserId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstName": "Unauthorized",
  "lastName": "Update"
}

### Update user with empty name (should fail with 400)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/{{adminUserId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstName": "",
  "lastName": "User"
}
